    <item>
      <title>Dollar Forwards的兴起为亚洲中央银行带来风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-16/rise-of-dollar-forwards-builds-risk-for-asia-s-central-banks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲的中央银行越来越多地利用衍生品来保护其货币免受强大的美元侵害，提出了有关他们可以这样做的时间以及他们是否只是在为未来储备麻烦的问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-16/rise-of-dollar-forwards-builds-risk-for-asia-s-central-banks</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Feb 2025 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>股权公牛冒着梦幻般的选举风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-16/equity-bulls-risk-sleepwalking-into-german-election-fueled-drop</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲的股票市场定价为德国联邦大选的近乎完美的结果。对于某些投资者来说，这增加了令人讨厌的惊喜风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-16/equity-bulls-risk-sleepwalking-into-german-election-fueled-drop</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Feb 2025 08:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>PBOC的PAN说，价格增长，消费“可以更强大”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-16/pboc-s-pan-says-price-growth-consumer-demand-can-be-stronger</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中央银行称，中国的价格增长和消费者的需求“可能会更强大”，因为国家的经济是合理的，而地方政府债务和房地产市场的风险降低了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-16/pboc-s-pan-says-price-growth-consumer-demand-can-be-stronger</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 16 Feb 2025 07:49:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
